Oyo State commissioner for environment and water resources Kehinde Ayoola is dead. He was reportedly sick for two weeks and died in Ibadan. The commissioner who hailed from Oyo town was the first Speaker of the Oyo State House of Assembly during the  era of Lam Adesina as Governor. Ayoola represented Oyo East state constituency between 1999 and 2003.  To enable commenting and other interactive features, please switch to the more advanced .